OL,3,CFlagship sites to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels
OL,6,FHousing in flagship sites - such as
OL,7,Fthe Bibby Stockholm barge - will cost
OL,8,Fthe government tens of millions of
OL,9,Fpounds more than using hotels,
OL,10,FWhitehall's spending watchdog has
OL,11,Fruled.
OL,13,FThe Home Office expects to spend #1.2
OL,14,Fbillion on housing asylum seekers in
OL,15,Flarge accommodation sites, the
OL,16,FNational Audit Office (NAO) said, with
OL,17,Flatest estimates suggesting an
OL,18,Finflated cost of #46 million.
