OL,3,CFlagship sites to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels
OL,6,FBut, so far, just two of the sites are
OL,7,Fopen - the Bibby Stockholm barge and
OL,8,FWethersfield - and were only housing
OL,9,Faround 900 people by the end of
OL,10,FJanuary, according to the watchdog's
OL,11,Ffindings.
OL,13,FMinisters have already scaled back the
OL,14,Fnumber of asylum seekers due to be
OL,15,Fhoused at the former RAF base in
OL,16,FLincolnshire from 2,000 to 800, while
OL,17,Fthe Home Office is also considering
OL,18,Fsimilar plans for Wethersfield,
OL,19,Faccording to the NAO's findings.
