OL,3,CFlagship sites to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels
OL,6,FThe department pursued the programme
OL,7,Fdespite "repeated" assessments that it
OL,8,F"could not be delivered as planned",
OL,9,FMr Davies warned as he called on the
OL,10,FHome Office to "reflect on lessons
OL,11,Flearned from establishing its large
OL,12,Fsites programme at speed and improve
OL,13,Fco-ordination with central and local
OL,14,Fgovernment given wider housing
OL,15,Fpressures".
