OL,3,CFlagship sites to house asylum seekers
OL,4,Ccost millions more than hotels
OL,6,FWhile the government has "made
OL,7,Fprogress" by cutting the number of
OL,8,Fhotels to house asylum seekers, and
OL,9,Fhad stopped using 60 by the end of
OL,10,FJanuary, it has "incurred losses and
OL,11,Fincreased risk" by "rapidly
OL,12,Fprogressing its plans to establish
OL,13,Flarge sites", the NAO said.
OL,15,F"The Home Office originally assessed
OL,16,Fthat large sites would be around #94
OL,17,Fmillion cheaper than hotels," the
OL,18,Fwatchdog added.
